display_name: Apnea-Hypopnea Index (Non-Supine): Apneas with >=5% oxygen desaturation and with or without arousal+ hypopneas with > 30% flow reduction and >=5% oxygen desaturation and with or without arousal / hour of sleep in non-supine position from type II polysomnography
calculation: 60 * ( hrop5 + hnrop5 + carop5 + canop5 + oarop5 + oanop5 ) / ( remepop + nremepop )
